title: The Latest: Cueto out with none out in 3rd inning of Game 3
text: > Top News The Latest: Cueto out with none out in 3rd inning of Game 3 Kansas City Royals starting pitcher Johnny Cueto, center, reacts as he's pulled from the game while third baseman Mike Moustakas, left, and second baseman Ben Zobrist look on during the third inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Championship Series against the Toronto Blue Jays on Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, in Toronto.
